snippet: The Jets have yet to determine who will suit up as Mark Sanchez’s backup, or his backup’s backup, positions of increasing import in case Sanchez falters again.
abstract: New York Jets coach Rex Ryan is peppered with questions about his decision to start quarterback Mark Sanchez and team's quarterbacking depth chart.
lead_paragraph: The Jets have yet to determine who will suit up as Mark Sanchez’s backup, or his backup’s backup, positions of increasing import in case Sanchez falters again.
